column16: James Loney grounds out, second baseman Ryan Roberts to first baseman Rusty Ryal.
Mike Hampton intentionally walks Matt Kemp.

Andre Ethier singles on a fly ball to right fielder Gerardo Parra.    Reed Johnson scores.  Ryan Theriot out at home on the throw, right fielder Gerardo Parra to second baseman Ryan Roberts to catcher Konrad Schmidt.   Jamey Carroll to 3rd on the throw.    Andre Ethier to 2nd.
Aubrey Huff pops out to catcher Miguel Montero in foul territory.
Mike Fontenot grounds out, second baseman Kelly Johnson to first baseman Adam LaRoche.
James Loney singles on a line drive to center fielder Chris Young.    Ryan Theriot scores.    Andre Ethier to 3rd.
Carlos Gonzalez singles on a line drive to left fielder Ryan Church.
Pedro Alvarez grounds out, second baseman Tony Abreu to first baseman Adam LaRoche.
Pedro Alvarez grounds out to first baseman Brandon Allen.
Eric YoungJr.   pops out to shortstop Stephen Drew.
Jonathan Herrera out on a sacrifice fly to center fielder Chris Young.    Ryan Spilborghs scores.
Andres Torres lines out to right fielder Gerardo Parra.
Michael Bourn grounds out, shortstop Stephen Drew to first baseman Adam LaRoche.
